         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, 23rd April 1880 ¶ Copy ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ In compliance with instructions received from the office of the Honorable the Chief Secretary, ¶ See W. Odgers to M, 19 April 1880(in this edition as 80-04...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">80.04.23</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James Patterson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">S80/4126, unit 1154, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS written by Georg Luehmann and signed by M.</p>
               </note>Melbourne, 23rd April 1880</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Copy</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In compliance with instructions received from the office of the Honorable the Chief Secretary,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See W. Odgers to M, 19 April 1880<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(in this edition as <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>80-04-19a).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have the honor to submit my views of the requirements of my Department as regards buildings during the financial year 1880-1881. I may be allowed to remark that during the last seven years no additional provision for buildings has been made for my departmental service, though I have not even office-rooms nor laboratory buildings ever since. Four years ago the sum of £900.-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was voted by Parliament, through the action of the Honorable J. Macpherson (then Chief Secretary) for the commencement of new building-accommodation in my Department,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Victoria</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Votes and Proceedings of the Legis</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">l</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">ative Assemb</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">l</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">y, session 1876</seg>, vol.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1, 28 November, p.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>174<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(under<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'Sundry works, Melbourne): ‘Extension and other Works, Botanical Museum, including fittings and furniture, £900-0-0’.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>which sum I allowed to lapse,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with a desire of seeing it doubled in the next financial year.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M had hoped to build a complete new building on 'new ground',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(M to J. MacPherson, 17 February 1877),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but was told that it was to be expended on an extension (W. Odgers to M, 12 February 1877).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>In M to J. MacPherson, 16 April 1877 (in this edition as 77-04-16a),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>he requested the sum of £1,800 for<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1877/1878 estimates.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>No provison was made in the estimates<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for that year<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>any<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>building work for the Government Botanist's Department.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>May I therefore hope that I may at least now recover the £900.-, saved then by the lapse of that sum to the revenue. I leave the consideration of this however entirely to your judgement, as the additional claims on the Treasury during the Exhibition-year<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>International Exhibition, Melbourne, 1880-1.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>may render it expedient to postpone the grant of building-votes for my departmental purposes for an other year.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn5" n="6">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation: 'Adhere to works'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Honorable the Commissioner of Public Works<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
         </div>
